description: NetconfSsh: Table recording Netconf/SSH configuration status for each cell, including timestamp, location, cell ID, and administrative state.  dateTime: Timestamp of the record; Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell; Id2: Redundant cell identifier; Id3: Unknown identifier; Id4: Unknown identifier; vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format; NetconfSsh.netconfSshId: Unique ID for the Netconf/SSH configuration; NetconfSsh.administrativeState: Administrative state (e.g., LOCKED, UNLOCKED); NetconfSsh.port: Port number used for Netconf/SSH.
